*Built-in Functions (Page 2 of 6)*

=== Core Communication ===
`echo message...` - Log/debug output in command response
`send target message...` - Send message to user or channel
  Target can be `@user, `#channel, a raw channel ID, or `#!` (current channel)
`sendi target text "label:macro" ...` - Send interactive buttons
`showui "title" "callback_macro" "field1" ...` - Open modal form

=== User and Channel Ops ===
`members #channel` - List members in channel
`addto @user1 @user2 #channel` - Invite users to channel
`kick #channel @user1 @user2` - Remove users from channel
`email @user` - Get email for user
`profile @user "display_name"` - Get profile field

=== Data and Utilities ===
`str value`, `strjoin sep list...`, `concat a b ...`
`length x`, `index list i`, `flatten list...`, `append list items...`
`range start end`, `map fn list`, `filter fn list`
`abs x`, `min ...`, `max ...`, `mod a b`

Use `/s7 help 3` for storage.
